    <name>
      <text>3.0.3 (Identify hypothesis even numbers)</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>Consider the following statement:</p>

<p> Let \(n\) and \(m\) be integers. Then if \(n\) and \(m\) are both even, then \(n+m\) is even.</p>

<p>Which of the following is the hypothesis of this statement?</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text/>
    </generalfeedback>
